(Ignore what Inferno said, for some reason he had no idea there was a 
deceased list, hehe.  There is in fact a deceased list)

Imprisoner/Predator/Choran/Chordate:



Imprisoner, Predator, and Choran ran, signatures to close for comfort, 
Predator firing a grenade from behind him at Hot Rod's tail pipe.

Running through the thick forest, two missiles passed by, exploding close, 
sending dirt and some shrapnel into the three bounty hunter's faces.  They 
continued onward as quick as they could go.

Predator went to his beast mode, the pain being subdued, the good clawing 
Savanna gave to him excruciatingly painful.

===

Chordate aimed his laser rifle at the back of Barrett's head, finger on the 
trigger.
"Identify yourself, or else I activate the autoguns and blow you back to the 
rebellion against the Quintessons, understand?"
